/**
 * Provides the scene graph node.
 *
 * Description:
 * The `dagon.graphics.entity` module provides the `Entity` class, which represents
 * a node in the scene graph and supports hierarchical transformations.
 *
 * Copyright: Timur Gafarov 2019-2026
 * License: $(LINK2 https://boost.org/LICENSE_1_0.txt, Boost License 1.0).
 * Authors: Timur Gafarov
